					.speaker-speaks 
						%span.speaker-text AMH: I have the original schedule still. The core design work was over 3 to 4 months, but the entire project lasted 9 months! As had become part of our core practice, and one Juhan has kept going over in Boston, we helped to build the things we designed. On the McAfee project, we did exactly that, and plenty of front-end code that Rob had written found its way into the shipping version of the product.
