					.speaker-avatar.ben
					.speaker-speaks 
						%span.full-name Ben Listwon:
						%span.speaker-text Yeah, McAfee was sort of the coming-of-age of the SV tech practice too. Rob and Tiff had really taken the wheel and I think the effort they put into really owning our development standards made it possible to meet the McAfee team where we needed to technically. They had a lot of low-level tech hurdles, and we had a high-level library of abstractions, so what could have gone horribly ended smooth sailing because of their hard work.
